msg: BEEHIVE-272: Replace usages of ControlAssemblyContext.createJavaOutputFile() with getSrcOutputDir()
BEEHIVE-209: Need ability to log warnings, errors etc for controls assembly
Removed the deprecated createJavaOutputFile() API, and replaced its usages with getSrcOutputDir().
Added a getMessager() API to the ControlAssemblyContext, which returns an apt Messager object impl
that control assemblers can use to log diagnostics.
